properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 2 at 3:16PM EST until February 3 at 5:00AM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 15 to 20 kt with gusts up to 25 kt and seas
3 to 5 feet expected.

* WHERE...Portions of Atlantic coastal waters.

* WHEN...From 11 PM this evening to 5 AM EST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 11 PM THIS EVENING TO 5 AM EST MONDAY
